data.description: $5k toward RATEBUYDOWN.Welcome to your new home! This recently refreshed property is a true standout in the market, offering both value and convenience.As you approach, notice the charming full front porch and tasteful stone accents that provide an inviting curb appeal. What sets this home apart is its recent updates, including a brand new roof and a freshly painted interior, ensuring you can move in worry-free.The spacious fenced yard is a perfect retreat for relaxation and outdoor activities, providing a safe and private space for you and your family.Unlike new construction homes that often come with unforeseen costs after closing, this property is move-in ready, saving you time and money. With its convenient location and thoughtful updates, it's a practical and smart choice for anyone looking for a hassle-free homeownership experience.  Seller is leaving the washer, dryer, and tv in the family room for the new owners.  Don't miss this opportunity to own a home that offers not only a fresh start but also the peace of mind that comes with a new roof and a welcoming, updated interior. Make it yours today!
